show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Lorenzo finds a photo of Jane in a fallen comrade’s belongings and vows to protect her, mistaking her for a war widow. Misunderstandings, jealousy, and betrayal drive them apart — until Jane uncovers a deadly conspiracy. When she’s trapped seeking revenge, Lorenzo returns, saves her, and proves their love can survive even the battlefield.
